Minesweeper
===========

This is a minimal version of minesweeper written in C with SDL2.
!! NEWLY ALSO DRAWS NUMBERS !!

Usage
-----
For detailed usage see `man 6 minesweeper`.

Supported flags are:
* -d <w> <h>	Specify minefield dimensions
* -h 		Prints usage and exits
* -m <n>	Specify number of mines
* -v		Prints version and exits

Building
--------
Run `make` to build and run `make install` (may require root) to install.
You may also run `make clean` to remove built files.
`make uninstall` (may require root) will uninstall the application

